  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.2">
<l>niṉaintu naintuḷ karainturuki yimaiyōr palaru muṉivarum</l>
<l>puṉainta kaṇṇi nīrcāntam pukaiyō ṭēnti vaṇaṅkiṉā</l>
<l>ṉiṉainta vellāp poruḷkaṭkum vittāy mutalil citaiyāmē</l>
<l>maṉañcey ñāṉat tuṉperumai mācū ṇātō māyōṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If, thinking, swooning, weeping [and] melting inside, the many unblinking ones and the sages</l>
<l>offer decorative chaplets, water [and] sandal with incense [and] bow,</l>
<l>with [you] as the seed of all matters thought of, in the beginning is there loss?</l>
<l>Will not your greatness of mind-made knowledge absorb [all] flaw, Dark one?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
